Package for laravle 5.* to deal with S3 rest api upload

To use
1、composer require Kify/S3

2、php artisan vendor:publish --provider="Kify\S3\S3ServiceProvider" --tag=config

3、config your S3 accessKey and secret in dictionary of app/config/s3.php

4、Add the package to your application service providers in config/app.php file.

'providers' => [

    /**
     * Third Party Service Providers...
     */
    Kify\S3\S3ServiceProvider::class,

],



Example:
$s3 = new \Kify\S3\S3();

$bucket = 'kify';
$path = 'test/';
$lifetime = 3600; 
$maxFileSize = (1024 * 1024 * 50);
$metaHeaders = [];
$requestHeaders = array(
    'Content-Type' => 'application/octet-stream',
    'Content-Disposition' => 'attachment; filename=${filename}'
);

$params = $s3::getHttpUploadPostParams(
    $bucket,		//your bucket name
    $path,			//the path of your upload，Can be empty ''
    $s3::ACL_PUBLIC_READ,		//file permission
    $lifetime,			//Period for which the parameters are valid
    $maxFileSize,		//max file size allow
    "http://fenke.timelink.cn/test.php", // callback url method get
    $metaHeaders,			//meta header 
    $requestHeaders,		//request header
    false // False since we're not using flash
);



